last_episode_to_air.name: A Goofy Fairy Tale
last_episode_to_air.overview: It's bedtime at the Clubhouse and everyone's ready for their favorite bedtime stories! Unfortunately, Goofy's magic trick makes all the stories disappear from the Clubhouse books!

name: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse
overview: Mickey and his friends Minnie, Donald, Pluto, Daisy, Goofy, Pete, Clarabelle and more go on fun and educational adventures.

episodes.name: Daisy Bo Peep
episodes.overview: We meet the gang again in a brand new educational television show for kids!

episodes.name: A Surprise for Minnie
episodes.overview: The gang prepares a special secret surprise for Minnie Mouse which makes her day.

episodes.name: Goofy's Bird
episodes.overview: There is much excitement when Goofy gets a cute pet bird.

episodes.name: Donald's Big Balloon Race
episodes.overview: The gang is bored so Donald comes up with a creative idea with a big balloon race!

episodes.name: Donald and the Beanstalk
episodes.overview: Donald runs in to a beanstalk and some weird thing take place.

episodes.name: Mickey Goes Fishing
episodes.overview: Goofy leaves his pet kitten, Mr. Pettibone, with Mickey, but Mr. Pettibone only eats big red gooey fish.

episodes.name: Donald the Frog Prince
episodes.overview: Donald turns into a frog prince.

episodes.name: Minnie's Birthday
episodes.overview: The group of friends celebrate Minnie's birthday and there are more surprises coming her way.

episodes.name: Goofy on Mars
episodes.overview: Goofy travels all the way to Mars.

episodes.name: Mickey-Go-Seek
episodes.overview: Mickey plays hide and seek with his friends but when Mickey hides really well, everyone gets worried about him

episodes.name: Daisy's Dance
episodes.overview: While attending a dance, Daisy gets stage fright when it is time for her to perform.

episodes.name: Pluto's Ball
episodes.overview: Pluto is outside playing with his favorite ball, when he bounces it a little too high and it rolls away. Mickey and Pluto set out to save the day and find the lost ball.

episodes.name: Mickey's Treasure Hunt
episodes.overview: Mickey believes that there is treasure somewhere and convinces all of his friends to search for it.

episodes.name: Daisy in the Sky
episodes.overview: Daisy, Pluto and Minnie are carried away by a bunch of balloons.

episodes.overview: Pluto starts baby-sitting Clarabelle Cow's puppies and soon realizes that they aren't as easy to watch as he thought they would be.

episodes.name: Pluto's Best
episodes.overview: Pluto and Butch, Pete's dog, compete for a trophy by playing a variety of games.

episodes.name: Mickey's Treat
episodes.overview: It's Halloween for Mickey and the gang and they get an invitation to go to Pete's Halloween Party located at the Trick-or-Treat Tower.

episodes.name: Minnie Red Riding Hood
episodes.overview: Minnie Mouse goes out into the woods and ventures across some trouble. Will her friends save the day?

episodes.name: Sleeping Minnie
episodes.overview: Minnie picks a magic rose that puts a curse on her that makes her sleep for 100 years if the spell is not broken.

episodes.name: Mickey Saves Santa
episodes.overview: Mickey and Donald run to save Santa Claus so that he can deliver the presents to everyone, otherwise there will be no Christmas.

episodes.name: Goofy the Great
episodes.overview: Goofy is performing in a magic show, but things start to go wrong right before the show is set to begin.

episodes.name: Mickey's Color Adventure
episodes.overview: Mickey's special Rainbow Color Machine runs into a problem when it starts to run out of color.

episodes.name: Goofy's Petting Zoo
episodes.overview: Goofy gets a job at the local petting zoo and falls asleep allowing the animals to escape. Goofy calls his pal Mickey to help him find the missing animals.

episodes.name: Doctor Daisy, M.D.
episodes.overview: Daisy acts as the doctor when Donald gets sick.

episodes.name: Donald's Lost Lion
episodes.overview: Donald can't find his favorite stuffed lion that he wants before bedtime. Mickey volunteers to help him find it.

episodes.name: Donald's Hiccups
episodes.overview: Donald gets a bad case of the hiccups. Daisy, Mickey, Goofy and Pluto all try to help him, but end up getting the hiccups themselves.

episodes.name: Fancy Dancin' Goofy
episodes.overview: When Clarabelle invites Goofy to go with her to the Fancy Dance, the gang helps him learn gentlemanly ways.

episodes.name: Mickeyâ€™s Handy Helpers
episodes.overview: When the handy Helpers break down, Mickey and the gang work to fix them.

episodes.name: Goofy the Home Maker
episodes.overview: Goofy and the gang construct a birdhouse for Baby Red Bird and his family

episodes.name: Goofy Baby
episodes.overview: When Professor Ludwig Von Drake's Time Machine turns Goofy into a baby, Mickey and the gang must babysit Goofy Baby until the machine is fixed.

episodes.name: Goofy in Training
episodes.overview: Goofy tries to run an obstacle course and gets help from his friends. Goofy is practicing for the Mickey Mouse Obstacle Course in hopes of winning a medal.

episodes.name: Minnie's Picnic
episodes.overview: Minnie decides to memorialize the new picnic area of the clubhouse by organizing the first picnic with the help of her friends.

episodes.name: Mickey's Big Band Concert
episodes.overview: Mickey and friends practice their band's music for the Mickey Park Polka-Palooza Dance Festival where the elephants will dance the Pachyderm Polka.

episodes.name: Minnie's Mystery
episodes.overview: Minnie attempts to find out who took her fresh baked muffins from the clubhouse.

episodes.name: Goofy's Hat
episodes.overview: Today is the Clubhouse's "Picture Day," where all of the Mickey Mouse Clubhouse friends get their picture taken. But it seems that Goofy is too disappointed to take his picture because he lost his hat.

episodes.name: Donald's Special Delivery
episodes.overview: The Clubhouse mail has arrived for all of the Clubhouse friends except Donald. It's up to the Clubhouse friends all make Donald feel better.

episodes.name: Daisy's Pet Project
episodes.overview: Daisy has trouble finding a pet for the Pet Parade. She must find a pet before the Pet Parade starts. She gets three pets, an elephant named Bubbles, a giraffe named Longfellow and a bunny named Captain Jumps-a-Lot.

episodes.name: Clarabelle's Clubhouse Carnival
episodes.overview: With Mickey and friends' help, Clarabelle sets up a carnival at the Clubhouse grounds. The reason for it is her need to feed the chickens with lots of corn.

episodes.name: Mickey and Minnie's Jungle Safari
episodes.overview: Minnie wants to have a picture of a hula hibiscus to complete her flower picture collection, but she has only one day to get it, when it is in full bloom. She will need help from all of her Clubhouse friends to get to where the flower is located.

episodes.name: Mickey's Round Up
episodes.overview: Ludwig Von Drake's package of wild numbers has arrived at the Clubhouse. However, they are accidentally let out and it is up to Mickey and his Clubhouse friends to don cowboy/cowgirl clothes and gear and round them all up to the "MickeyCorral" on the grounds before the Professor returns from an errand. Note: This is the only time something is alive.

episodes.name: Mickey's Big Job
episodes.overview: Mickey and the gang take care of Willie the Giant's farm while he's away.

episodes.name: Mickey's Comet
episodes.overview: Everyone wants to view Mickey's Comet, but first they have to find Professor Von Drake and his telescope. This was the second episode in the series, following 'Doctor Daisy, M.D.', that the 'Mystery Mousketool' was chosen first.

episodes.name: Mickey's Camp Out
episodes.overview: Mickey and the rest of the Clubhouse friends have a \"Big Clubhouse Camp Out. They are trying to earn a Clubhouse Camp Out badge for each one of them by doing two tasks at a campsite.

episodes.name: Mickey's Art Show
episodes.overview: Goofy learns to sculpt, paint and draw so he can compete in an arts-and-crafts show sponsored by Mickey.

episodes.name: Choo-Choo Express
episodes.overview: Mickey and the gang build a train, so they can carry the professor's non-melting snow to the Clubhouse.

episodes.name: Mickey and the Enchanted Egg
episodes.overview: A story Mickey plans to read aloud about an enchanted egg, suddenly becomes real. The big purple dragon egg Wizard Pete is taking care of, rolls out of the castle and into Donald and Goofy while they are walking to the Clubhouse. A purple baby dragon pops out of the egg. Mickey and friends name it Zoe and take it to Wizard Pete, while trying to get out of his traps.

episodes.name: Pluto's Bubble Bath
episodes.overview: Clarabelle and Bella are coming over for tea and biscuits and dog biscuits and Pluto is all dirty and needs a bubble bath. But when Pluto's bubble bath gets out of hand, Mickey and Pluto each get stuck inside a giant bubble and float away from the clubhouse.

episodes.name: Goofy Goes Goofy
episodes.overview: Goofy gets cloned after Professor von Drake's new experimental Gooey-Goo splashes onto him. Mickey and his friends must take care of the clones until the effect wears off.

episodes.name: Space Captain Donald
episodes.overview: Donald leads the gang on a mission to the moon to retrieve Pluto's bouncy ball.

episodes.name: Secret Spy Daisy
episodes.overview: Daisy protects Clarabelle's secret recipe for oatmeal raisin cookies from Pete.

episodes.name: Mickey's Silly Problem
episodes.overview: The clubhouse's "silly switch" gets stuck and makes everyone act in comical ways, such as Mickey only speaking in rhyme and Pluto making every animal sound except barking.

episodes.name: Minnie's Rainbow
episodes.overview: Minnie searches for a pot of gold and meets a leprechaun after a rainbow appears over the clubhouse.

episodes.name: Pete's Beach Blanket Luau
episodes.overview: Mickey and his friends throw a beach party to cool off on the hottest day of the year and Pete invites everyone.

episodes.name: Pluto's Playmate
episodes.overview: Mickey and his friends help Salty the Seal do tricks for the circus.

episodes.name: Sir Goofs-a-Lot
episodes.overview: Goofy wants to be knighted by Queen Clarabelle, so he proves his bravery by going on a quest to retrieve three items.

episodes.name: Mickey's Thanks A Bunch Day
episodes.overview: Minnie uses a growth spray in her garden to help her fruits and vegetables grow in time to be picked for Thanks A Bunch Day, but it turns them all into gigantic creations.

episodes.name: The Friendship Team
episodes.overview: Help Detective Minnie and Secret Spy Daisy search for missing party hats for the clubhouse's Friendship Day celebration.

episodes.name: Goofy's Coconutty Monkey
episodes.overview: When Goofy's friend Coco the Monkey can't find any coconuts for her "coconutty party," Goofy, Mickey and the clubhouse gang take a trip into the jungle in search of coconuts.

episodes.name: Pluto to the Rescue
episodes.overview: Pluto comes to the rescue when Donald and Goofy build a snowman so big, they can't climb around it or over it.

episodes.name: Clarabelle's Clubhouse Mooo-sical
episodes.overview: Clarabelle stages a musical about nursery rhymes starring chickens from the petting zoo, but they practice so much, they lose their voices.

episodes.name: Mickey's Message from Mars
episodes.overview: Mickey, Daisy, Goofy and Pluto fly up to Mars and help a Martian Mickey find a secret treasure.\n\nGuests - Ludwig Von Drake, Pete, Martian Mickey and Pluto from Pluto.

episodes.name: Donald's Ducks
episodes.overview: Donald helps a group of ducks get to a warm beach for their winter retreat.

episodes.name: Mickey's Adventures in Wonderland
episodes.overview: A mechanical cuckoo bird that's a birthday gift for Daisy flies away, and the gang embarks on an imaginative Alice in Wonderland-like adventure to retrieve it.

episodes.name: Goofy's Super Wish
episodes.overview: Goofy trains to be a superhero and uses his skills after Clarabelle's moo-muffin maker breaks.

episodes.name: Mickey's Big Surprise
episodes.overview: Help Mickey and his friends solve the five Fun Puzzles to get a Big Surprise.

episodes.name: Minnie-s Bee Story
episodes.overview: A strong wind has blown Buzz-Buzz the Bee away from his sunflower!

episodes.name: Goofy's Goofbot
episodes.overview: Goofy constructs a robot in his own likeness.

episodes.name: Mickey's Springtime Surprise
episodes.overview: Mickey and Minnie kick off the first day of spring with an egg hunt.

episodes.name: Super Goof's Super Puzzle
episodes.overview: Goofy becomes Super Goof to solve some puzzles laid out by Pete.

episodes.name: Donald of the Desert
episodes.overview: The Clubhouse's sandbox is empty, so Donald leads the gang into the desert to get more sand. But they stumble across much more than that.

episodes.name: Happy Birthday Toodles
episodes.overview: It is Toodles' birthday and the whole gang is there to celebrate.

episodes.name: Goofy's Magical Mix-Up
episodes.overview: When Goofy The Great makes Pluto's dog house disappear, it's up to Mickey and the gang to find it.

episodes.name: Pluto's Dinosaur Romp
episodes.overview: The Professor accidentally brings back a baby dinosaur while using his time machine.

episodes.name: Minnie's Pajama Party
episodes.overview: Minnie throws a pajama party for all her friends.

episodes.name: Road Rally
episodes.overview: Mickey and his pals participate in a road rally that takes them across sandy deserts, over snow-covered mountains and through lush jungles.

episodes.name: Donald the Genie
episodes.overview: Pete The Genie gives Donald genie powers so that he can make his friend's wishes come true.

episodes.name: Daisy's Grasshopper
episodes.overview: Mickey and the gang have to find Daisy's pet grasshopper Wilbur so that the Professor can take his picture for Grasshopper Day.

episodes.name: Mickey's Mousekersize
episodes.overview: Mickey and the gang help Pete get in shape by Mousekersizing.

episodes.name: Mickey's Little Parade
episodes.overview: Mickey and his pals search for three wind-up toy musicians after they run about due to being wound too tight just before a parade appearance.

episodes.overview: Minnie opens a boutique filled with a variety of bows and bow ties.

episodes.name: Minnie's Masquerade
episodes.overview: Minnie decides to have a masquerade ball.

episodes.name: Goofy's Giant Adventure
episodes.overview: Goofy goes on a quest for a magical elixir to cure Willie The Giant's tummy ache.

episodes.name: Mickey's Show and Tell
episodes.overview: Martian Mickey visits the clubhouse for a show-and-tell presentation.

episodes.overview: Minne and Daisy arrive at the clubhouse with Goldie the goldfish. However, Goldie is all alone and has no one to swim with so Daisy and Minnie decide take Goldie to the waterfall in the jungle to find a friend.

episodes.name: Space Adventure
episodes.overview: Mickey, Minnie, Donald, Daisy, Goofy and Pluto blast off to outer space.

episodes.overview: Donald cares for a lost egg, while his friends search for its family.

episodes.overview: Super Mickey and the Clubhouse Heroes must work as a team.

episodes.overview: Kansas City Mickey returns to help the clubhouse team solve a mystery in the Hidden Jungle.

episodes.overview: Mickey and the gang are prepared to rock with a battle-of-the-bands showdown filled with epic guitar solos.

episodes.name: Donald Jr.

episodes.overview: Mickey and the gang search for something at the bottom of Mickey Lake. Mickey and the gang use a submarine to explore Mickey Lake, when Professor Von Drake's sonar-detecting machine discovers that there's something big at the bottom.

episodes.name: Mickey's Pirate Adventure
episodes.overview: Mickey and pals are enjoying a day at the beach when Peg Leg Pete delivers a note from Goofyâ€™s long lost Grandpappy, Captain Goof-Beard, asking for the gangâ€™s help in ensuring that Harmony-Chord Island, the musical isle where Goof-Beard lives, doesnâ€™t go completely out of tune and sink.

episodes.name: Mickey's Happy Mousekeday
episodes.overview: It's Mickey's birthday, and for his birthday present, the Clubhouse gang has organized fun activities for the big Mousekeday.

episodes.overview: Mickey has birthday and his friends help him at the ceremony.

episodes.overview: Mousekedoer malfunctions and needs to be fixed.

episodes.overview: Mickey, Minnie and Pluto stumble upon Count Mikula's castle and help solve the mystery of its creaky noises.

episodes.overview: When Minnie is invited to sing at Mistletoe Mountain, Mickey discovers that all the instruments are missing.

episodes.overview: Mickey helps Goofy serve up deliveries from his "Chef Goofy On the Go" lunch truck.

episodes.overview: Professor Von Drake is working on a surprise invention when he discovers that he is missing four of his tools. Toodles helps Mickey find them with Mouseketools and a checklist.

episodes.overview: Put on your sneakers, sports fans! Today is the first ever Mickey Mouse Sport-a-thon! It's an action-filled sports tournament that draws athletes from around the Clubhouse.

episodes.overview: Minnie's on her way to Mars on an urgent mission! Her assignment? Help her outer space twin, Martian Minnie, host a tea party for our Clubhouse friends throughout the galaxy!

episodes.overview: It's bedtime at the Clubhouse and everyone's ready for their favorite bedtime stories! Unfortunately, Goofy's magic trick makes all the stories disappear from the Clubhouse books!
